<text top="1087" left="1208" width="970" height="63" font="font3" id="p1_t59" reading_order_no="58" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">The  left  portion  displays  the  distribution  over  areas  of </text>
<text top="1143" left="1210" width="963" height="58" font="font5" id="p1_t60" reading_order_no="59" segment_no="5" tag_type="text">the  number  of  publications  and  of  citations  using </text>
