<text top="1298" left="1261" width="911" height="62" font="font6" id="p1_t63" reading_order_no="62" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">Knowledge  also  flows  in  scientific  activities  such  as </text>
<text top="1352" left="1210" width="962" height="58" font="font5" id="p1_t64" reading_order_no="63" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">communication  between  collaborators.  The  environ- </text>
