<text top="1557" left="1210" width="962" height="62" font="font6" id="p1_t68" reading_order_no="67" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">and  displays  the  evolution  of  the  flows  to  help  assess </text>
<text top="1615" left="1210" width="963" height="55" font="font1" id="p1_t69" reading_order_no="68" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">the  teamwork’s  effectiveness,  for  example,  whether </text>
